{
  "stem": "22047.6",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And, and they-- we went there and were treated like absolute heroes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know, I talked about being a reluctant hero earlier [INAUDIBLE], but this was-- they treated us like we were some kinds of gods.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This one lady said-- of course, we were walking down to the dining room, I guess.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she said to my wife, your husband was a liberator?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she said, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In what camp?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she said, Dachau.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she said she was a, a survivor from Belsen, I believe it was.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, and she said, I kiss the ground of this country every day.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And without people like your husband, I wouldn't be able to do that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we had this testimony by these several survivors, and then quite a story by one of them that was in Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She happened to be in, I guess, a satellite camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because she was standing in the doorway of this factory and saw this vehicle coming down the hill.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it had a white star on it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this person jumped out of the-- of the Jeep.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was an American officer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he came running down to there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she was standing in the doorway.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she said, 'Ich bin Juden.' And he said, 'So am I!' [LAUGHS] And so he was her liberator, and they were married a year later in Paris.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Yeah, what a story.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And she's-- in her testimony, she said, without you-- people like you-- I wouldn't be able to rock my grandchildren.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I wouldn't have been able to marry this fine man that I'm married to.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I wouldn't have-- I wouldn't have survived for another 50 years.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
